 ed media\, from any country and at any career stage. Apply via the Light W
 ork SlideRoom portal.\n\nOrganisation: Light Work\nLocation: Syracuse\, Ne
 w York\, USA (in-person\, one-month residency on site)\nAward: $7\,500 sti
 pend plus a furnished apartment and access to state-of-the-art photography
  facilities. The residency concludes with a feature in a special edition o
 f 'Contact Sheet: The Light Work Annual' alongside a commissioned essay. N
 o application fee.\nDuration: One-month residency in 2027\n\nMore: https:/
 /lightwork.slideroom.com
