 ard: Two non-restrictive tiers: $1\,000 Individual Artist Micro-Grants (fo
 r artist educators and emerging visual artists working toward their first 
 major exhibitions)\, and $2\,000 Community Organization Micro-Grants (for 
 producing organizations with an annual budget under $500\,000 providing fr
 ee public arts programming in the Austin area). Funds can be used at the r
 ecipient's discretion. No application fee.\nDuration: One-time award\n\nMo
 re: https://a3austin.org/2026-27-micro-grants/
